Package: graniteR
Type: Package
Title: Interface to IBM Granite Embedding Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Skander Tahar Mulder", email = "skandermulder@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Provides a pipe-friendly interface to IBM's Granite embedding models
    via Python's transformers library. Supports sentence embeddings, text classification,
    and fine-tuning workflows following tidyverse conventions.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    reticulate (>= 1.41),
    dplyr,
    tibble,
    rlang
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    readr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/skandermulder/graniteR
BugReports: https://github.com/skandermulder/graniteR/issues
